        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Rapid Response to Climate Impacts Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of State to establish a Climate Impacts Task Force, which must seek to prevent and mitigate the potential for national security risks arising from climate change and related social conditions.</p>]]>
        </text>
